item.title: Test Blog Part 3!
item.description: This is my 4th blog attempt. I am keeping this piece unedited to show my thought process back in 2018. Note I am no longer on Jekyll or using the Minimal Mistakes theme I ask myself that all too much. This is the 3rd blog I try(4th if you count tumblr… I don’t) in earnest to start. And it’s been up in some capacity since September, without updates, so even before I get it in a decent state I already feel like I failed(I talk more about my view on failure Here).
